Text: Special MSDN Flash Microsoft Developer Days Special MSDN Flash All the developer news from Microsoft in one email For more information tools and community resources visit MSDN Online at This is a one time only copy of the MSDN Flash newsletter To begin receiving the MSDN Flash on an ongoing basis registering via Microsoftcom Profile Center INFOhelpfaqhtm Dear Dev Days Event Attendee As a previous attendee to Dev Days we are extending you a special offer to take advantage of discount pricing for the upcoming Microsoft Developer Days Register through October and a colleague gets in for free Use mail code EPC Coming to US cities on November and you can take advantage of this opportunity in a local city near you Dev Days is your best opportunity to get firsthand insights on Visual StudioNET development using the latest tools and technologies from Microsoft To view indepth descriptions of the sessions visit eventsdevdayssessionsasp All attendees will receive a copy of the Visual StudioNET release candidate indepth reference materials including the presentations and demos shown in the days sessions training modules and other exciting giveaways In addition to all this and the special pricing all attendees are eligible to win a Microsoft XBox Game System one per city Register today eventsdevdays and provide mail code EPC Or to view your own interactive POPgram invitation visit indexaspCIDampTIDGOWV You have received this special offer as part of the MSDN flash which helps developers stay up to date with the latest development news from Microsoft Sent every other week in a single comprehensive email this free newsletter contains pointers to all the latest resources products betas services packs SDKs and more To register for this free resource sign up via Microsoftcom Profile Center INFOhelpfaqhtm This is the only email you will receive from the MSDN Flash unless you choose to register There is nothing you need to do to unsubscribe If you are unable to access your special POPgram invitation please visit the Microsoft DevDays web site directly at eventsdevdays How to use this mailing list If you would prefer to not receive any future email communications for Dev Days either click mailtoEAECADDFEB ewslettersMicrosoftcomsubjectUNSUBSCRIBE to send an unsubscribe email or reply to this message with the word UNSUBSCRIBE in the Subject line To stop all email newsletters from microsoftcom either click mailtoEAECADDFEB ewslettersMicrosoftcomsubjectSTOPMAIL to send your request or reply to this message with the word STOPMAIL in the Subject
